  (@custom "contractspecv0" (after data) "\00\00\00\00\00\00\01vInitialize the lending pool contract\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `env` - The Soroban environment\0a* `pool_admin` - Address with pool admin privileges\0a* `emergency_admin` - Address with emergency admin privileges\0a* `price_oracle` - Address of the price oracle contract\0a* `treasury` - Address of the treasury (receives protocol fees)\0a* `dex_router` - Address of DEX router (Soroswap router)\00\00\00\00\00\0ainitialize\00\00\00\00\00\06\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0apool_admin\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0femergency_admin\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0cprice_oracle\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\08treasury\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0adex_router\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\13incentives_contract\00\00\00\03\e8\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\12KineticRouterError\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\93Supply assets to the protocol\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `env` - The Soroban environment\0a* `caller` - The address calling this function\0a* `asset` - The address of the underlying asset to supply\0a* `amount` - The amount to be supplied\0a* `on_behalf_of` - The address that will receive the aTokens\0a* `_referral_code` - Code used to register the integrator (unused for now)\0a\0a# Returns\0a* `Ok(())` - Supply successful\0a* `Err(KineticRouterError)` - Supply failed due to validation or cap limits\0a\0a# Cap Enforcement\0aThis function enforces supply caps if configured. Caps are stored as whole tokens\0aand converted to smallest units during enforcement to maximize the effective range.\00\00\00\00\06supply\00\00\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06caller\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\05asset\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06amount\00\00\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0con_behalf_of\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0e_referral_code\00\00\00\00\00\04\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\12KineticR