eiver contract must implement `execute_operation` callback.\0a\0a# Parameters\0a- `initiator`: Address initiating the flash loan (must authorize)\0a- `receiver`: Contract that will receive the loan and execute callback\0a- `assets`: Assets to borrow\0a- `amounts`: Amounts to borrow for each asset\0a- `params`: Arbitrary data passed to receiver\0a\0a# Receiver Callback\0aThe receiver must implement `execute_operation` with the standard flash loan interface.\0a\0a# Authorization\0aInitiator must authorize the call, but anyone can be an initiator.\0aThe receiver handles its own authorization logic.\0a\0a# Errors\0a- `InvalidFlashLoanParams`: Invalid parameters\0a- `InsufficientLiquidityForFlashLoan`: Not enough liquidity\0a- `FlashLoanExecutionFailed`: Receiver callback failed\0a- `FlashLoanNotRepaid`: Loan not fully repaid\00\00\00\0aflash_loan\00\00\00\00\00\05\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\09initiator\00\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\08receiver\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06assets\00\00\00\00\03\ea\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\07amounts\00\00\00\03\ea\00\00\00\0a\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\06params\00\00\00\00\00\0e\00\00\00\01\00\00\03\e9\00\00\03\ed\00\00\00\00\00\00\07\d0\00\00\00\12KineticRouterError\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\02\1dFlash liquidation - atomic liquidation using flash loan\0a\0a# Arguments\0a* `liquidator` - Address of the liquidator (must be authorized)\0a* `user` - Address of the user being liquidated\0a* `debt_asset` - Address of the debt asset\0a* `collateral_asset` - Address of the collateral asset\0a* `debt_to_cover` - Amount of debt to cover\0a* `collateral_to_seize` - Amount of collateral to seize\0a* `min_swap_out` - Minimum amount of debt asset to receive from swap\0a* `deadline` - Transaction deadline timestamp\0a\0a# Returns\0a* `Ok(())` if liquidation successful\00\00\00\00\00\00\11flash_liquidation\00\00\00\00\00\00\08\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0aliquidator\00\00\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\04user\00\00\00\13\00\00\00\00\00\00\00\0ade